class=title>   Swordbreaker...</span><hr size=1> About the Swordbreaker, I'm sure most of you have heard about it.  I am hoping to find someone with firsthand experience with this blade to explain a few things:<br>
<br>
First: I heard a rumor that it can only be equipped in either your offhand or your mainhand.  Is this true?  If so, which hand, offhand or mainhand? Being able to dual wield them would be nice.<br>
<br>
Second: How rare?  How many people out there have them? I've heard it's a drop of the Spectral Knight in Karnors. Of course, it's NO DROP for some stupid reason so in order to get one (or two) I'd have to camp for it.  I hate Karnors! <p><img src="http://www.valorblade.com/dantes2.jpg" width="305" height="138"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/ubrontothunderfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bronto Thunderfoot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(8/18/00 10:50:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Swordbreaker...</span><hr size=1> I saw it dropped off the spectral protector in Karnor's, Obidiah was with us and he got this sweet weapon, give him a tell and I'm sure he can fill you in on the info =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dantes>Dantes</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://forums.eqrealms.com/ubb/icons/icon10.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(8/18/00 3:46:04 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.valorblade.com/dantes.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Swordbreaker...</span><hr size=1> Thanks.  I did see Obidiah in the game and I confirmed that this weapon works in either hand, so you could dual wield it.  But I still haven't figured out if there's even a slightest chance someone could actually obtain 2 of these fine weapons.  From what it sounds like, I have a snowball's chance in hell.  Sounds like the protector isn't a really deep spawn, but he's a rare one, I've never seen it myself and been in Karnors many many hours.  On top of that when or if he even did spawn, there would be 2 or 3 other groups that might pull it instead of my own.  And to top that off, the drop itself seems extremely rare. <p><img src="http://www.valorblade.com/dantes2.jpg" width="305" height="138"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/utumagok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tumagok</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>   <font color=#CC9900>(8/28/00 8:12:41 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.d-f-a.org/tuma.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Swordbreaker...</span><hr size=1> we got one from VS lair gaurdian<br>
